title: DDFP 354: Top young QBs & L.T. on NBA playoffs
itunes:title: DDFP 354: Top young QBs & L.T. on NBA playoffs
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and LaDainian Tomlinson to discuss the most exciting players to watch in the NFL and an update on the NBA playoffs. Shek also ranks his top 5 young quarterbacks (42:01).
